=======================================================================
                              READ ME
=======================================================================

                 THIS IS A PRE ALPHA VERSION - v0.0!

=======================================================================

Where to start:

run TorweltenEditor.py

folders:

../
chars/      character directory
data/       basic data
fonts/      included fonts
ui_img/     UI images
templates/  template files for PDF export

the program is coded in python 3 (3.6 - should run fine 3.4+)

beyond the standard library you'll need:
* PIL (oder Pillow) -> pip install pillow
* reportlab -> pip install reportlab

=======================================================================

to compile a windows version please run:
> python setup.py py2exe
[only 3.4 right now!]